column5: Local tv news said that there was a loose floating dock near Johnson's beach in Lake Simcoe.
I ran up the holland river last weekend and it was like running an obstacle course with all the wood in the water
Police hauled it in before noon today... unless this is another dock ..
They once "reported" about the results of a world championship triathlon that had happened 4 weeks before but was shown that day on another network.
Never know... I heard on the radio around noon.. as I was staring at the mass of jockeying boats in the narrows..that the police had hauled it off already.
